<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ideed388f7-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s1604"><num value="1604">§ 1604.</num><heading> Publication</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">After judgment by the court, or the issuance of a cease and desist order, in any case arising under this chapter, notice thereof shall be given by publication in such manner as may be prescribed in the rules and regulations made and promulgated under this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ideed388f8-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1939-08-09/ch615">Aug. 9, 1939, ch. 615</ref>, title IV, § 414, <ref href="/us/stat/53/1289">53 Stat. 1289</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
